cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.SD 

The paper discusses the use of bibliometric techniques to enhance retrieval processes in digital libraries, which is closely related to the field of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the use of statistical modelling and network analysis, which are common techniques in digital libraries (cs.DL) and social network analysis (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the use of these techniques for specific communities (cs.CY) and large, cross-domain collections (cs.SD).
